OL,3,CCo-op thief arrested as Met say retail
OL,4,Ccrime is 'spiralling out of control'
OL,6,FThis CCTV footage shows the shocking
OL,7,Fmoment a shoplifter was caught in a
OL,8,Ftargeted Metropolitan Police operation
OL,9,Fin south London, following multiple
OL,10,Freports of theft from the store.
OL,12,FDerek Bell, 36, was caught on camera
OL,13,Fin the Lower Marsh Co-op ransacking
OL,14,Fthe meat chiller on 27 January.
OL,16,FThat same day, the Metropolitan police
OL,17,Farrived at the supermarket early and
OL,18,Fwaited in the back office, monitoring
OL,19,FCCTV cameras.
