OL,6,FWhen Bell began raiding the meat
OL,7,Ffridge, the officers immediately
OL,8,Fdetained and arrested him.
OL,10,FBell, of no fixed address, pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty the following day to two counts
OL,12,Fof shoplifting at Croydon Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt. He was jailed for eight weeks.
OL,15,FInspector Darren Watson, from the
OL,16,FNeighbourhood Policing Team in
OL,17,FLambeth, said "This is an excellent
OL,18,Fexample of how the Met is taking a
OL,19,Ftargeted approach to tackle the type
OL,20,Fof offending that matters most to
OL,21,FLondoners.
