OL,6,F"We know shoplifting has a significant
OL,7,Fimpact on businesses and shop staff.
OL,8,FIt often also fuels other crime and
OL,9,Fanti-social behaviour.
OL,11,F"In Lambeth alone, our enforcement
OL,12,Factivity means 11 of the 14 most
OL,13,Fprolific shoplifters in the area are
OL,14,Fcurrently in prison and we will
OL,15,Fcontinue to take action against those
OL,16,Fwho cause misery in our communities."
