OL,6,FRetail crime is "spiralling out of
OL,7,Fcontrol" at more than 2,000 incidents
OL,8,Fa day, according to the latest figures
OL,9,Ffrom the British Retail Consortium
OL,10,F(BRC).
OL,12,FThe amount spent on crime prevention
OL,13,Fis also at a record high, with
OL,14,Fretailers investing #1.8 billion on
OL,15,Fmeasures such as CCTV, more security
OL,16,Fpersonnel, anti-theft devices and body
OL,17,Fworn cameras, up from #1.2 billion the
OL,18,Fprevious year.
